{
  "texts": [
    "Relatedly, \"singletonness\" also refers to a relative feature, with a singleton being defined as the only stimulus with a particular absolute feature among other stimuli.",
    "The central bars in Fig. 3a-c are clear examples of singletons.",
    "The one in Fig. 3c, for instance, is a singleton in color but not in orientation.",
    "Figure 3d -f illustrate less straightforward cases.",
    "The central bar in Fig. 3d is a singleton, but is not particularly salient."
  ]
}